      "name": "Astrology & Gemstones ",
      "settings": {
        "about_heading": "Ultimate Guide On Gemstone Jewelry For Zodiac Signs",
        "about_text": "Jewelry has had a greater significance than merely being a decorative or fashionable component of society for centuries. It has also been desired for its substantial cultural, religious, and astrological significance. One that symbolises wealth, strength of spirit, and connection to the divine.",
