    "information_content_info_UdVRhi": {
      "type": "information-content-info",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_x9RfYr": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Impact of Astrological Jewelry on Everyday Life",
            "heading_level": "h2",
            "heading_id": "impact",
            "alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "richtext_yprzB6": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>If you’re someone who checks the daily horoscope today, or looks for zodiac signs personality traits every time you fall in love, you should consider getting a subtle stones jewelry piece. A piece that resonates with your birth sign dates can help amplify your strengths and protect you against negative energies and challenges. The connection of astrology, jewelry, and gems has existed for history at least thousands of years. Often, ancient kings and queens wore crowns and ornaments made of grand gemstones that symbolized wealth, power, and divine protection. Even contemporary sadhus and yogis carry many of these same gemstones along with rudraksha malas for chakra energy healing. The main concept when gifting gemstones is that they are given with the intention that the gemstone is aligned with cosmological energies. Jewelry and astrology overlap in that the materials used for jewelry - such as gems and metals - are more than physical decorative inflections. They are materials that resonate with cosmic frequencies and have the ability to influence energy in many different aspects of one’s life. Whether you are wearing a gemstone ring, a zodiac pendant, or an auspicious wedding ring, you are not only embracing contemporary beauty but also a piece of cultural and cosmic wisdom. In summary, astrological and zodiac jewelry symbolises the relationship between the beauty of the jewelry and the belief behind it, the marriage of traditional and modern ideas, and, of course, represents your identity and alignment to cosmological energies.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
