          }
        },
        "richtext_mYqbkM": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Astrology divides the annual monthly calendar into twelve zodiac signs. Each sign is ruled by a specific planet that resonates with certain elements relevant to that sign<span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">.</span> These astrological signs, or star signs, are believed to impact our behaviour, personality, relationships, and even destiny. Usually, gemstones worn complement the positives and negatives of your sun sign. Today, jewellers even design collections specifically to highlight the individuality of these zodiac signs. For example, in recent times, Leo star sign jewellery and Capricorn pendants are popular picks. Zodiac jewellery goes a long way in blending personal style and spiritual belief. Let’s explore every zodiac sign, its traits, and recommended jewelry to complement them. </p>"
          }
        }
      },
